00:04:19.697 --> 00:04:21.407
What do you plan to do next?

00:04:27.705 --> 00:04:28.873
What can we do?

00:04:29.374 --> 00:04:30.333
Just wait.

00:04:31.250 --> 00:04:32.335
For how long?

00:04:32.919 --> 00:04:36.464
What if you wait until his execution,
and he still won't do the interview?

00:04:36.547 --> 00:04:37.882
What will you do about this film?

00:04:42.428 --> 00:04:45.890
Gosh. It's not your first time
filming a documentary, is it?

00:04:47.934 --> 00:04:50.561
Shitty things like someone
declining an interview aren't new.

00:04:51.145 --> 00:04:53.648
There are ways to film
without an interviewee.

00:04:53.731 --> 00:04:54.982
Why are you so worried?

00:04:59.862 --> 00:05:00.822
Ta-wei.

00:05:01.322 --> 00:05:04.200
Look, you haven't received
a single subsidy for your film.

00:05:04.283 --> 00:05:06.536
