and the rent here.

00:05:18.297 --> 00:05:21.384
Don't be so willful.
You always go for the unprofitable films.

00:05:21.467 --> 00:05:23.928
Are you done yet, Liu Chien-yi?

00:05:24.595 --> 00:05:26.222
You keep talking about money.

00:05:27.598 --> 00:05:29.267
If you're scared of losing money,

00:05:29.350 --> 00:05:33.563
you shouldn't have fucking become
a filmmaker in the first place!

