00:06:04.594 --> 00:06:09.515
Fuck. You're more suited to being
a freeloading scammer than a director.

00:06:10.683 --> 00:06:12.935
All right, why don't you two…

00:06:13.019 --> 00:06:14.020
Shut up.

00:06:15.021 --> 00:06:16.647
I haven't even brought up Yu yet.

00:06:16.731 --> 00:06:17.857
Me?

00:06:18.858 --> 00:06:22.403
Back then, you said the company
had to hire someone to be our assistant.

00:06:22.487 --> 00:06:23.404
And now?

00:06:23.905 --> 00:06:25.990
