00:09:28.964 --> 00:09:30.966
Mrs. Li.

00:09:31.717 --> 00:09:33.427
Here, take a look.

00:09:35.638 --> 00:09:37.223
It's what you asked me to film.

00:10:17.471 --> 00:10:19.098
Here's the last question.

00:10:20.683 --> 00:10:22.727
You've been here for so many years.

00:10:23.227 --> 00:10:25.062
Do you miss your mom?

00:10:30.860 --> 00:10:33.904
Then… do you have anything

00:10:34.405 --> 00:10:36.365
