00:11:06.687 --> 00:11:08.814
So… Mrs. Li,

00:11:08.898 --> 00:11:11.525
I did what you asked.

00:11:12.276 --> 00:11:16.280
Does that mean you'll let us film?

00:11:19.492 --> 00:11:22.620
Can I watch it again?

00:11:23.204 --> 00:11:24.079
Of course.

00:11:47.102 --> 00:11:49.313
So, Mrs. Li,

00:11:49.396 --> 00:11:51.816
you mentioned earlier

00:11:51.899 --> 00:11:54.860
that Jen-yao didn't have
a good relationship with his dad.

00:11:54.944 --> 00:11:58.864
Can you tell us more about
what his dad was like?

00:12:06.664 --> 00:12:12.545
He… wasn't that bad in the beginning.

00:12:13.254 --> 00:12:16.882
During his better days,
he treated us very well.

00:12:17.758 --> 00:12:18.801
He would

00:12:19.468 --> 00:12:22.805
drive us to the seaside

00:12:22.888 --> 00:12:25.015
and take us out for delicious food.

00:12:25.099 --> 00:12:28.018
Then things didn't go well at work,

00:12:28.102 --> 00:12:30.062
so he started drinking.

00:12:30.145 --> 00:12:32.648
He kept drinking more,

00:12:32.731 --> 00:12:34.400
and his mood kept getting worse.

00:12:35.568 --> 00:12:39.613
I don't know
exactly when he started beating me.

00:12:40.239 --> 00:12:44.243
But in the beginning,
he didn't beat Jen-yao.

00:12:46.036 --> 00:12:47.621
Later on,

00:12:48.330 --> 00:12:52.126
Jen-yao couldn't stand it
and wanted to shield me.

00:12:52.209 --> 00:12:55.129
That's when his dad got angrier

00:12:55.212 --> 00:12:57.047
and started beating Jen-yao.

00:13:01.927 --> 00:13:06.557
Mrs. Li, you said in your police statement

00:13:06.640 --> 00:13:10.394
that you and Li Jen-yao
were abused at home for over ten years.

00:13:12.062 --> 00:13:14.815
Didn't you ever consider
fighting back during that time?

00:13:18.527 --> 00:13:19.820
Fight back?

00:13:23.532 --> 00:13:24.867
