I wouldn't know where to go.

00:13:39.757 --> 00:13:40.966
I had no choice.

00:13:41.050 --> 00:13:42.176
So

00:13:42.760 --> 00:13:45.304
I just let him beat me as he pleased.

00:13:45.387 --> 00:13:47.389
