00:13:58.651 --> 00:14:00.235
He's the son.

00:14:00.319 --> 00:14:02.154
How can a son hit his dad?

00:14:02.237 --> 00:14:07.701
So I would grab Jen-yao and stop him.

00:14:07.785 --> 00:14:09.286
I'd just let his dad beat me.

00:14:09.370 --> 00:14:12.790
It'd all be fine
when he sobered up, right?

00:14:12.873 --> 00:14:15.000
That'd be the end of it.

00:14:15.501 --> 00:14:18.754
A son can't beat his dad,
no matter what, right?

00:14:40.609 --> 00:14:42.611
Do you all think…

00:14:45.781 --> 00:14:47.449
Jen-yao is where he is today

00:14:48.409 --> 00:14:49.827
because of me?

00:14:52.454 --> 00:14:54.289
Jen-yao used to be so well-behaved,

00:14:54.915 --> 00:14:56.583
respectful…

00:14:58.752 --> 00:15:00.504
and considerate.

00:15:03.257 --> 00:15:06.260
