we can call it a day here.

00:16:48.320 --> 00:16:51.573
Why don't we find another time
to finish this up?

00:16:52.157 --> 00:16:53.659
Wasn't today good enough?

00:16:53.742 --> 00:16:54.868
I…

00:16:54.952 --> 00:16:57.412
If today was okay, then that's enough.

00:16:57.496 --> 00:16:58.914
-I don't--
-Mrs. Li.

00:16:58.997 --> 00:17:02.334
It's really all right.
Don't talk about it if you don't want to.

00:17:02.417 --> 00:17:04.503
We won't film anymore either, okay?

00:17:04.586 --> 00:17:05.754
So how about this?

00:17:05.838 --> 00:17:09.675
If you want to talk to someone
about this in the future,

00:17:09.758 --> 00:17:13.011
or if you think you can continue filming,

00:17:13.095 --> 00:17:14.096
then call me, okay?

00:17:15.013 --> 00:17:16.056
Did you hear that?

00:17:16.849 --> 00:17:17.808
Pack up our things.

00:17:17.891 --> 00:17:20.018
I'll go for a smoke
and bring the car around.

00:19:43.578 --> 00:19:44.621
What are you doing?

00:19:49.251 --> 00:19:50.294
Mrs. Li.

00:19:51.753 --> 00:19:52.838
Mrs. Li.

00:19:53.839 --> 00:19:56.133
Do you know this girl next to Li Jen-yao?

00:19:56.216 --> 00:19:57.592
No, I don't.

00:19:57.676 --> 00:19:59.219
What's with you? Let's go.

00:19:59.303 --> 00:20:00.637
Hold on.

00:20:00.721 --> 00:20:02.055
Then what about this CD?

00:20:02.139 --> 00:20:03.432
Does this belong to him?

00:20:05.600 --> 00:20:09.146
I brought back this CD
when I went to tidy up his place in Taipei

00:20:09.229 --> 00:20:12.107
