00:20:38.008 --> 00:20:38.884
Miss,

00:20:39.384 --> 00:20:41.303
we're filming a documentary.

00:20:42.179 --> 00:20:43.221
We're not detectives.

00:20:43.805 --> 00:20:46.892
-I just really want to know who she is.
-So who is she to you?

00:20:46.975 --> 00:20:48.894
How is this your business?
Do you know her?

00:20:49.811 --> 00:20:51.646
I don't know
if you'd consider it knowing her.

00:20:57.611 --> 00:20:59.279
You know that girl?

00:21:06.036 --> 00:21:08.038
