00:21:35.899 --> 00:21:40.195
that the female ghost looked up Li Jen-yao
after she'd possessed you.

00:21:40.278 --> 00:21:42.114
Is all that true? You didn't lie to me?

00:21:42.197 --> 00:21:43.573
I swear.

00:21:46.284 --> 00:21:48.120
Why would I lie to you?

00:21:48.745 --> 00:21:52.249
