why this female ghost came to me.

00:21:52.916 --> 00:21:56.169
But I just found out she and Li Jen-yao
went to the same high school.

00:21:56.920 --> 00:21:58.213
Then it clicked.

00:21:58.296 --> 00:21:59.506
Can you get to the point?

00:22:02.259 --> 00:22:04.428
According to all the information,

00:22:04.511 --> 00:22:06.388
besides Wang Yu-hsiang's wife and child,

00:22:06.471 --> 00:22:08.557
