were Li Jen-yao's classmates.

00:22:09.474 --> 00:22:11.226
So now you suspect

00:22:11.726 --> 00:22:14.771
that this female ghost
was someone killed by Li Jen-yao too?

00:22:19.901 --> 00:22:21.486
I don't know.

00:22:27.159 --> 00:22:28.577
Let me tell you.

00:22:29.953 --> 00:22:31.621
Go back to Taipei on your own first.

00:22:32.247 --> 00:22:35.876
Tell Chien for me
that I'm staying here for a few more days.

00:22:36.376 --> 00:22:37.377
Why?

00:22:38.128 --> 00:22:41.673
