00:24:48.341 --> 00:24:49.426
Chou Pin-yu.

00:24:53.096 --> 00:24:54.222
Bye.

00:25:03.898 --> 00:25:05.108
This is good enough.

00:25:05.609 --> 00:25:06.860
I want to go back now.

00:25:07.652 --> 00:25:09.487
Wait, I have one more question.

00:25:14.451 --> 00:25:17.120
A few days ago, I visited your mom.

00:25:19.414 --> 00:25:21.916
I found this photo sticker in your room.

00:25:27.255 --> 00:25:29.090
What was your relationship with her?

00:25:38.725 --> 00:25:40.518
My intuition tells me

00:25:41.478 --> 00:25:43.772
that you probably did what you did

00:25:44.439 --> 00:25:46.066
because of this girl.

00:25:52.364 --> 00:25:53.823
You have a wild imagination.

00:25:55.533 --> 00:25:57.285
