Do you really want to know?

00:32:52.200 --> 00:32:53.534
Li Jen-yao!

00:33:01.334 --> 00:33:04.545
Didn't you see me wave to you just now?

00:33:13.596 --> 00:33:15.348
You clearly saw me.

00:33:15.848 --> 00:33:17.058
Why did you ignore me?

00:33:23.523 --> 00:33:24.357
Hsiao-tung.

00:33:25.900 --> 00:33:26.984
Yun-chen?

00:33:27.735 --> 00:33:28.861
What is it?

00:33:32.865 --> 00:33:34.992
Yun-chen, where are you dragging me?

00:33:36.119 --> 00:33:37.620
How did you and Li Jen-yao meet?

00:33:41.707 --> 00:33:46.254
Well… we were going to have lunch
on the rooftop one day, remember?

00:33:46.337 --> 00:33:48.089
But the student union held you up.

00:33:48.172 --> 00:33:50.383
He happened to be there that day.

00:33:50.466 --> 00:33:52.301
We chatted a little
and got to know each other.

00:33:53.553 --> 00:33:54.512
What is it?

00:33:54.595 --> 00:33:56.514
Why are you suddenly so serious?

00:33:56.597 --> 00:33:57.932
I'm being serious right now.

00:33:58.015 --> 00:33:59.475
You'd better stay away from him.

00:33:59.559 --> 00:34:01.394
Li Jen-yao isn't as simple as you think.

00:34:01.477 --> 00:34:03.271
What do you mean?

00:34:03.354 --> 00:34:06.566
You know Ouyang Ti?
The one you keep turning down.

00:34:07.400 --> 00:34:09.235
I know him. What about it?

00:34:10.528 --> 00:34:11.696
In our freshman year,

00:34:11.779 --> 00:34:13.739
Ouyang Ti and a few boys

00:34:13.823 --> 00:34:15.783
had a beef with Li Jen-yao
for some reason.

00:34:15.867 --> 00:34:17.451
They had a brawl in the restroom.

00:34:17.535 --> 00:34:19.287
You know how ruthless Li Jen-yao was?

00:34:19.370 --> 00:34:21.581
Chuang Jung-tai ended up in the hospital.

00:34:21.664 --> 00:34:22.915
He even got a few stitches.

00:34:23.791 --> 00:34:25.001
Is that true?

00:34:25.084 --> 00:34:26.377
Of course it's true.

00:34:26.460 --> 00:34:28.462
It caused a big stir.

00:34:28.546 --> 00:34:31.215
Li Jen-yao got one major
and one minor demerit afterwards.

00:34:31.299 --> 00:34:32.592
He nearly got expelled.

00:34:34.552 --> 00:34:35.386
But

00:34:36.470 --> 00:34:39.223
we weren't the ones involved in the fight.

00:34:40.057 --> 00:34:41.934
Who's to say who was right or wrong?

00:34:42.018 --> 00:34:43.978
Maybe Li Jen-yao wasn't the problem.

00:34:44.729 --> 00:34:46.397
Anyway, don't talk to him anymore.

00:34:46.480 --> 00:34:49.066
Pretend you don't know him.
Save yourself from trouble.

00:34:49.859 --> 00:34:54.197
Isn't daily dance practice tiring enough?
Why waste your time on someone like him?

00:34:55.615 --> 00:34:56.824
Yun-chen,

00:34:57.533 --> 00:34:59.118
we've known each other forever.

00:34:59.202 --> 00:35:01.579
I've never heard you say
anything bad about anyone.

00:35:02.079 --> 00:35:03.915
Do you hate Li Jen-yao so much

00:35:03.998 --> 00:35:05.750
because he did something to you?

00:35:06.959 --> 00:35:08.920
Or is it just because of these rumors?

00:35:15.718 --> 00:35:18.054
Time for class.
I don't want to talk about it anymore.

00:35:18.137 --> 00:35:20.097
I'm heading back. You should hurry too.

00:35:20.181 --> 00:35:21.599
Hey, Lai Yun-chen!

00:35:27.855 --> 00:35:29.607
OCEAN DRAGON SEAFOOD

00:35:30.775 --> 00:35:32.443
Here are your stir-fried clams.

00:35:36.822 --> 00:35:38.407
Welcome. Sit wherever you want.

00:35:42.245 --> 00:35:43.996
I'm feeling pretty depressed now

00:35:44.580 --> 00:35:47.166
because your mom and I had an agreement.

00:35:47.667 --> 00:35:50.002
-Boss.
-She was supposed to bring me money today.

00:35:51.963 --> 00:35:53.047
But then?

00:35:56.092 --> 00:35:57.635
It's already been four hours.

00:35:57.718 --> 00:36:00.471
She hasn't shown up,
and she's not answering her phone.

00:36:01.597 --> 00:36:02.431
What now?

00:36:02.515 --> 00:36:04.976
Did she copy your dad's bad habits?

00:36:05.059 --> 00:36:06.894
Standing hooligans up on purpose?

00:36:06.978 --> 00:36:10.564
Or does she think
they are all good people?

00:36:11.774 --> 00:36:13.276
It's no use coming to me.

00:36:13.359 --> 00:36:15.361
I have no money. Please leave.

00:36:17.488 --> 00:36:19.824
Don't be so scared of me.

00:36:19.907 --> 00:36:22.118
Every time you see me,
you try to make me leave.

00:36:22.618 --> 00:36:24.453
Actually, we really pity you.

00:36:24.537 --> 00:36:26.831
You're so unlucky
to have parents like that.

00:36:27.331 --> 00:36:30.668
So I came today to help you.

00:36:32.295 --> 00:36:33.546
I want to give you a chance.

00:36:34.630 --> 00:36:37.049
A chance for you
to quickly pay off your debt

00:36:37.133 --> 00:36:40.052
and cut ties with your brute of a dad.

00:36:42.221 --> 00:36:44.056
From now on, when you're at school,

00:36:44.140 --> 00:36:45.599
sell amulets for me

00:36:45.683 --> 00:36:47.435
to keep your classmates safe.

00:36:48.394 --> 00:36:52.148
You decide if this is sold as cigarettes
for $50 each

00:36:52.231 --> 00:36:54.025
or in packs for $1,000.

00:36:54.108 --> 00:36:56.610
If you want to do this,

00:36:57.236 --> 00:36:58.487
I'll help all the way

00:36:58.571 --> 00:37:00.781
and cover the upfront costs for you.

00:37:03.534 --> 00:37:05.411
I won't sell drugs at school for you.

00:37:12.293 --> 00:37:14.086
Hey. Don't go too far

00:37:14.170 --> 00:37:15.546
or I'll call the police.

00:37:15.629 --> 00:37:17.048
Sir, come.

00:37:17.131 --> 00:37:19.342
Here's a little something for you.
Go smoke in the back.

00:37:19.842 --> 00:37:20.676
Go.

00:37:24.096 --> 00:37:27.600
I could be your enemy and hurt you

00:37:27.683 --> 00:37:30.019
or be your savior and help you.

00:37:30.102 --> 00:37:31.562
Your choice.

00:37:31.645 --> 00:37:32.730
Okay?

00:37:32.813 --> 00:37:33.647
Here.

00:37:37.985 --> 00:37:40.363
To keep you safe.

00:37:40.905 --> 00:37:41.739
Here you go.

00:37:44.867 --> 00:37:46.160
Let me know.

00:37:50.206 --> 00:37:51.290
Wang, come.

00:37:56.087 --> 00:37:57.713
Get out of the way.

00:38:09.683 --> 00:38:11.685
MAY YOU BE SAFE

00:38:21.946 --> 00:38:25.366
Jen-yao, here's the thing.
You've worked hard these past few months.

00:38:26.242 --> 00:38:29.161
-But today, the customers--
-Boss, don't worry.

00:38:32.832 --> 00:38:34.375
I won't make this hard for you.

00:38:36.585 --> 00:38:38.129
Today is my last day.

00:38:39.380 --> 00:38:42.007
Thank you for looking out for me
these past few months.

00:38:50.349 --> 00:38:52.518
EXQUISITE LODGING FOR RENT

00:39:04.488 --> 00:39:06.991
Jen-yao, how come you're back?
Don't you have work?

00:39:08.492 --> 00:39:09.368
Where are you going?

00:39:11.954 --> 00:39:15.666
A friend in Taipei got a last-minute puja
and wants my help for a few days.

00:39:15.749 --> 00:39:17.168
Here.

00:39:18.252 --> 00:39:19.587
Money.

00:39:22.756 --> 00:39:23.716
Here.

00:39:24.717 --> 00:39:25.718
Take the money.

00:39:26.677 --> 00:39:27.678
Remember to eat.

00:39:27.761 --> 00:39:28.888
Don't stay up late.

00:39:28.971 --> 00:39:30.639
Spend the money wisely.

00:39:33.851 --> 00:39:35.352
Are you going alone?

00:39:37.688 --> 00:39:38.564
Of course.

00:39:39.148 --> 00:39:41.901
I don't know
where your dad has run off to.

00:39:41.984 --> 00:39:43.861
I haven't seen him since yesterday.

00:39:47.323 --> 00:39:50.075
I have to go now or I'll miss my bus.

00:39:50.159 --> 00:39:51.535
Take good care of yourself.

00:39:52.203 --> 00:39:53.245
Remember that.

00:41:13.158 --> 00:41:14.159
Hello?

00:41:15.244 --> 00:41:17.079
Is that Jen-yao?

00:41:18.122 --> 00:41:19.290
What's wrong?

00:41:20.958 --> 00:41:22.710
You're lying to me, aren't you?

00:41:23.961 --> 00:41:25.379
What are you saying?

00:41:27.047 --> 00:41:28.799
Why would I lie to you?

00:41:31.343 --> 00:41:32.511
You're lying to me.

00:41:33.012 --> 00:41:34.763
You're not going to a friend's.

00:41:37.308 --> 00:41:38.892
You won't be coming back.

00:41:38.976 --> 00:41:40.311
You want to abandon me.

00:41:48.736 --> 00:41:51.280
How could I possibly abandon you?

00:41:51.363 --> 00:41:52.531
Don't be paranoid.

00:41:52.615 --> 00:41:55.492
I'm really going to Taipei
to help a friend.

00:41:55.576 --> 00:41:56.994
I'll be back soon.

00:41:57.077 --> 00:41:59.496
Don't be paranoid. Be good.

00:42:01.248 --> 00:42:02.416
Where are you?

00:42:02.958 --> 00:42:04.460
Come back first, okay?

00:42:04.960 --> 00:42:06.128
Who are you talking to?

00:42:06.712 --> 00:42:07.671
Jen-yao?

00:42:08.964 --> 00:42:11.050
Don't tell him too much.

00:42:11.133 --> 00:42:14.386
Who knows if he'd give away our location?

00:42:15.012 --> 00:42:16.889
Have you thought about me?

00:42:17.473 --> 00:42:19.016
What they would do to me?

00:42:19.808 --> 00:42:21.644
How could you be so selfish?

00:42:23.270 --> 00:42:25.606
Jen-yao, you…

00:42:26.732 --> 00:42:28.817
Don't be like this.

00:42:29.693 --> 00:42:32.029
It'll be fine. Listen to me.

00:42:32.529 --> 00:42:33.781
If they come to you,

00:42:33.864 --> 00:42:36.825
just tell them that we're not home.

00:42:37.326 --> 00:42:38.702
Don't open the door either.

00:42:39.203 --> 00:42:41.330
They won't do anything to you.

00:42:44.291 --> 00:42:45.250
Mom.

00:42:47.086 --> 00:42:48.504
I'm begging you, okay?

00:42:48.587 --> 00:42:49.963
Can you come back?

00:42:54.843 --> 00:42:56.887
Just leave him, will you?

00:42:58.681 --> 00:42:59.598
Come back.

00:43:00.099 --> 00:43:01.392
I'll take you away.

00:43:01.975 --> 00:43:03.435
You can go wherever you want.

00:43:03.936 --> 00:43:05.396
I'll make money and support you.

00:43:06.563 --> 00:43:08.315
Leave him, all right?

00:43:09.608 --> 00:43:10.693
Please.

00:43:11.819 --> 00:43:13.570
Listen to me this once, will you?

00:43:15.614 --> 00:43:17.533
Listen to me just this once, okay?

00:43:48.480 --> 00:43:50.899
What do you want to tell him?

00:43:52.609 --> 00:43:55.612
I don't think this is right.

00:43:55.696 --> 00:43:56.530
Let's go back.

00:43:57.614 --> 00:43:59.366
Are you out of your mind?

00:43:59.450 --> 00:44:02.327
Don't forget that your name is
on the promissory note too.

00:44:02.411 --> 00:44:05.831
If we go back now,
we're putting our lives in Big K's hands.

00:44:06.540 --> 00:44:07.833
It's better to run away now

00:44:07.916 --> 00:44:10.461
than to have your son
arrange a funeral for us, okay?

00:44:18.218 --> 00:44:20.888
If… we're not there,

00:44:21.597 --> 00:44:23.932
they wouldn't do anything
to Jen-yao, would they?

00:44:24.016 --> 00:44:26.685
Don't worry.
Nothing will happen to Jen-yao.

00:44:36.487 --> 00:44:38.489
FROM TAICHUNG TO TAIPEI

00:54:32.916 --> 00:54:37.921
